anesh loves these little steamed dumplings that are made of a translucent rice flour pastry, and stuffed with a mixture of sweetened coconut and jaggery. And I do too! Though mawa modak is also as amazing, these white beauties win hands down. Divine indulgence for sure! ","rating":"0","votes":"0","slideimage_crops":[{"id":"16264534","slideimage_id":"5846674","slide_id":"442120","type":"original","url":"http:\/\/i.huffpost.com\/gadgets\/slideshows\/442120\/slide_442120_5846674_original.jpg"},{"id":"16264536","slideimage_id":"5846674","slide_id":"442120","type":"free","url":"http:\/\/i.huffpost.com\/gadgets\/slideshows\/442120\/slide_442120_5846674_free.jpg"},{"id":"16264538","slideimage_id":"5846674","slide_id":"442120","type":"smallfree","url":"http:\/\/i.huffpost.com\/gadgets\/slideshows\/442120\/slide_442120_5846674_smallfree.jpg"},{"id":"16264540","slideimage_id":"5846674","slide_id":"442120","type":"small","url":"http:\/\/i.huffpost.com\/gadgets\/slideshows\/442120\/slide_442120_5846674_small.jpg"},{"id":"16264542","slideimage_id":"5846674","slide_id":"442120","type":"splash_900","url":"http:\/\/i.huffpost.com\/gadgets\/slideshows\/442120\/slide_442120_5846674_splash_900.jpg"},{"id":"16264544","slideimage_id":"5846674","slide_id":"442120","type":"splash_600","url":"http:\/\/i.huffpost.com\/gadgets\/slideshows\/442120\/slide_442120_5846674_splash_600.jpg"},{"id":"16264546","slideimage_id":"5846674","slide_id":"442120","type":"splash_small","url":"http:\/\/i.huffpost.com\/gadgets\/slideshows\/442120\/slide_442120_5846674_splash_small.jpg"},{"id":"16264548","slideimage_id":"5846674","slide_id":"442120","type":"sq50","url":"http:\/\/i.huffpost.com\/gadgets\/slideshows\/442120\/slide_442120_5846674_sq50.jpg"},{"id":"16264550","slideimage_id":"5846674","slide_id":"442120","type":"croppable","url":"http:\/\/i.huffpost.com\/gadgets\/slideshows\/442120\/slide_442120_5846674_croppable.jpg"},{"id":"16264552","slideimage_id":"5846674","slide_id":"442120","type":"compressed"